                        <item xml:id="a0_4960">
                           <locus target="#3v">-3v</locus>
                           <q xml:lang="ar">هذه الصلوت لسيدنا خضر عليه السلام من قرأها مرة لا يسئله الله من قليل ذنبه ولا كثير ومن قراها ه</q>
                           <desc>Colophon</desc>
                           <note>Short identification of text 2r - 3v as a group of prayers ascribed to al-Ḫadir which will absolve the reader of his sins.
Written in black script at the bottom center of the page.</note>
                           <note>
                              <p>
            See also <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS1115IHA">الخضر</persName>
                              </p>
                           </note>
